<h2>Access to electronic resources</h2>
<p>In Books & more search results can be filtered by choosing the available online choice. Click on a title to get direct access to the electronic full-text.</p>
<p>Articles & more offers the following options for full-text access:</p>
<p><i class="fa fa-external-link"></i> get-it: links directly to the full-text.</p>
<p><i class="fa fa-external-link"></i> SFX-Services: links to full-text access via the SFX menu. If no full-text is available alternative ordering options become available.</p>
<p>Access to electronic full-text from outside the university network is restricted for private customers. Nevertheless, via <i class="fa fa-external-link"></i> SFX-Services it is possible to order a copy of the text from your library (for a fee, see <a href="<?= $this->url('help-page', array('topic' => 'delivery')); ?>"><?= $this->transEsc('helppage.delivery') ?></a>).</p>
<p>Students and staff members of universities of Basel and Bern can connect to the university network via VPN from anywhere (<a href="<?= $this->redirectProtocolWrapper()->getWrappedURL('http://mobile.unibas.ch') ?>" target="_blank">Basel</a>, <a href="<?= $this->redirectProtocolWrapper()->getWrappedURL('http://unibe.ch/university/campus_and_infrastructure/rund_um_computer/internetzugang/access_to_internal_resources_via_vpn/index_eng.html') ?>" target="_blank">Bern</a>).</p>
